\id 2TH
\ide  UTF-8
\h 2 Abhathesalonike 
\toc1 2 Abhathesalonike 
\toc2 2 Abhathesalonike 
\toc3 2th 
\mt1 2 Abhathesalonike  
\c 1
\cl Ulyango 1 
\p
\v 1 U Paulo nu Silwano, nu Timotheo, shibhanza mwa Ngolobhe nudada wetu nu gosi uYesu Kilisti.  
\v 2 Uwene ubhe hulimwi nurutengano afume hwa Ngolobhe udada uwetu nugosi uYesu UKristi.  
\v 3 Ihwanziwa husalifye Ongolobhe ensikuzyoti hulimwi bhaholo. Eshisashi hwaziwa hwahuje mkula mlugano lwenyu hwa wowoti mwonjelelaje owinji.  
\v 4 Ntente tiyanga ahwilole mmabhanza ga Ngolobhe. tiyanga entumi eyewene yamlinayo eyemayemba gonti tiyanga enongwa enzya mayemba gamvumilila.  
\v 5 Evi vifyani efya logwe nalyoli nu Ngolobhe ashilile ega mbhaziwa ahwinjile bhuumwene waNgolobhe husababu yamwene mpate amayemba  
\v 6 Hwahuje halali alipwe nu Ngolobhe abhapele amayemba bhala bhabhaye vya amwe,  
\v 7 nabhapele asogwe amwe mwemyemba pandwemo namwe aibhomba ega paibhoneha Ogosi uYesu paifuma amwanya pandweemo nuhala uzelu neguvu zyake.  
\v 8 Mhanti yaluhozwo abhabha sombe ashisasi bhala bhabhasaga bha mwenye Ongolobhe nabhala bhabha sagahozya iizuu ilya Gosi wetu U Yesu.  
\v 9 Bhaipata amayemba nabudwe wilawila bhezabhe hutalii nugosu otuntumu ni ndandi lyakwe.  
\v 10 Aivomba ensiku lyaihwinza ayemeshelwa navantuvakwe vwaisagogwawoti bhabhaposheye. Nulusimisizyo lwake lwamanyishe hulimwi.  
\v 11 Hwahuje tibhaputila ensiku zwoti tilabha huje Ngolohe wetu bhabhaziwe huje bhamanyene akwiziwe. Tilabha huje ubhombe ahantu ahinza nambombo iyewene nenguvu.  
\v 12 Tibhalabha huje lyemehwaje itawa lya Gosi u Yesu tilabha huje ayemewaye umwene mwenee Ongolobhe nu Gosi U Yesu Kilisti.   
\c 2
\cl Ulyango 2 
\p
\v 1 Eshi ahunze hwa Yesu uBwana wetu U Yesu UKiristi awunganya, tikhale peka numwene: tihuwalavya amwe muwaholo wetu,  
\v 2 aje msahatamiwe nantele msahayaziwe nalinali hu Mpepo au hunongwa, hukalata, yilolehana aje isiku ilia Bwana tayari lyezeli.  
\v 3 Umntu asahahopela hwidala lyolyonti sagalihueza lila lyagwe umuntu wimbiwilifumile shoti awoneshe, uola umwana wi mbiwi.  
\v 4 Uno yuyola azinjila nantele ahuilola hahonti hahaputwa. Hahafumila epo, akhala mshiwamnza isha Ngolobhe ahuilolesya umwene awanji yu Ngolobhe.  
\v 5 Mwe, saga mkumbuha aje lwanahali namwe nahawawozyezye humambo eegaa?  
\v 6 Eshi mmenye shishi huzuwila aje aoneshe isiku ziakwe lwaliafia.  
\v 7 Isiri yula umuntu wimbiwi awomba imbombo eshu, aleho yazijila eshi mpakalwa haiepa mwidala.  
\v 8 Oula umiwi lwahaiwa pazelu ubwana Yesu ahaibuda nu moyela wilomu lyakwe. UBwana ahaimwomba awe saga hantu hohoti nufunuo wahuenza hwakwe.  
\v 9 Ahunzeala umiwi ihaiwa mbombo ya shetani hungovu zyonti, ishiwonesho, na amawonesho gilenkha,  
\v 10 ilenka lyonti liwalangani amambo eego gahaiwa hwa wala wawate ujile, huje sangawaposheye ulugano wa liolioli sangawakombolelwe ewo.  
\v 11 Shesho Ungolobhe ahuwapela imbombo yili ni mbiwi aje weteshe ilenka.  
\v 12 Haha fumila epo huje wahailongwa, wala wasagateshe lioli awene wahasongwezye uwalangani.  
\v 13 Eshi ihuaziwa husalipye Ungolobhe hani amwe muwaholo mganilwe nu Bwana. Huje uBwaan ahawasaluye amwe muwe wahuande akombolewe kwa uwoziwa wa Umpepo nulweteho wa lioli.  
\v 14 Eli lyanahawa hakwizizye amwe ashirile izwi muwajie akawe utundumu wa Bwana Yesu UKristi.  
\v 15 Mwe wahalo, emelelaji shinza umanyaji ulautamaduni mmanyiziwe hwizwi ni karata zyetu.  
\v 16 Eshi, U Bwana witu U Yesu UKristu yeyo mwene nu Nngolobhe, udaada wetu yatuganile na hutipele uwila nudandamazu uwinza uwakhale uuhuenza ashilile wene,  
\v 17 awasowelezye na gombe amoyo genyu, ashilile inzuri ni mbombo inyinza.   
\c 3
\cl Ulyango 3 
\p
\v 1 Iishi bhiholo tulabhilaji huje ezyo lya dada liwezye abhale wonti nabhwimishilye shalishili payoo hulimwi.  
\v 2 Labhaji aje tukomboshe afume humbivyi nabhantu ambambivyi wahuje sagabhunti abha ulyeteho.  
\v 3 Lelo uGosi ahwitishilya, wayisisimizya amwa nagulila afume mwola ubhivyi.  
\v 4 Tulinguvhu nuGosi ulemwe aje abhomba mwayendela abhombe antele mwayendelela abhombe egatubhalajizya.  
\v 5 Ugosi awezye alongozye amoyo ginyuu mlugano wijivyi ubhuu waKilisti.  
\v 6 Eshitubhalajizya, bhiholo mmuli tawalyakwe uBwana Yesu Kilisti, huje mmwepushe ula uholo ula akhala maisha igiwolo sagiisho gagafumina nahapango hasa mwa poshile hulintee.  
\v 7 Phipo amwi mminye huje mwigajegatubho mbaanti. Hagatakhalaga pokanamwe nishibhala bhasabhanishoga.  
\v 8 Hagatalyanga ahatolu hammuntu yayunti hagatasombelega afumeepo twabhombaga embombo usiku na pasanya humbo hummwile lishile umuntu amwe.  
\v 9 Twabhomba esho hagahuje satani lyawamle twabhomba esho ili tubheshineshe luhulimwi mutudaje ati.  
\v 10 Lwatwali pamopenena mwitwabhalajizye, “Khashele umuntu ayasabhomba embombo angandeelye.”  
\v 11 Muhati umuo tuhuvhwa ajee bhamoo wawilibha bhalinuwolo pomlisho amwe habhabhomba embombo wantu mbatiho.  
\v 12 Ishi bho tuvhalajizya nasamizye Bwana Yesu Kristu, ilazimihahuje ulamtu abhombaje imbombo na pummemyee na lye shalye shao vhivhoo.  
\v 13 Lelo amwi, bhiholo, mungande azilishe amoyo abhombe ganalyoli.  
\v 14 Khashele mutu yayunti hagawanza ehuvye izyo lwitu umu mkalata ene. Muvhe maso nawo mugande sangane nabhi ili akenye.  
\v 15 Muganda humwejele ajelugu lelo msundaje nishi hwiholo.  
\v 16 Ugosi uluvyano nyunyo apele lubhano pahati amadala gunti Ugosi avhe na mwe mwenthi.  
\v 17 Ululamuho lwani ni Paulo hukhono gwani nene, ambashoshimanyilo hukalata ishi simba.  
\v 18 Mwoyi ngwadada wetu U Yesu Ukristi iwezye abhenamwe mwindei.   